On that note, as an aside to Virginia residents,  I recently read in an
industry trade paper that in Virginia, vehicles over 25 years old will soon
be exempted from emissions inspection.  This means that most (and in a few
years, all) busses will be exempt.  Previously the cutoff was 1968.

