Yes, the 25 year exemption is in effect in Virginia.  Now.

But, if the VW required a cat converter because it was a California bus, it 
will need one in Virginia to pass the Safety Inspection.

Also, the EGR FILTER is a requirement for the FI buses, California or not!!  
Safewty Inspection again.

The Emmissions Inspection looks for the EGR VALVE!!

